2010-1?-??: Toonloop 1.9.7
--------------------------

This release is an unstable version in the 1.9 series. This version contains new features and bug fixes preparing the 2.0 stable series. 

New features:
    * Add the --max-images-per-clip option. Default is 0. (infinity)
    * Add the --intervalometer-rate option
    * Add the --enable-intervalometer option
    * Add the --layout option
    * Use a messaging queue for the OSC callbacks
    * Added the --remove-deleted-images option


Bug fixes: 
    * Fixed a crash when the OSC interface was enabled.
    * Fixed an crash when the OSC interface was disabled.

